<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4412361>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 84−89. Amphialycus (Orthacarus) oblongus (Halbert). 84—Genital valve of male, 12 genital setae per valve, 7 pairs of eugenital setae; 85—Tritonymph, venter, 11 genital setae per valve; 86—Deutonymph, venter, 4 genital setae per valve; 87—Protonymph, venter, 1 genital seta per valve; 88—Larva, ventral habitus, holotrichy, genital valves absent; 89—Larva, dorsal habitus, holotrichy. 76−89 from RSA, near Potchefstroom." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4412361/files/figure.png" .

